narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: The library is entirely inadequate for its collection and for its policies (especially that students are only allowed to borrow one book at a time for one day). This was not an impediment for this course, but it should be an absolute embarrassment for the school. Otherwise, everything was beyond satisfactory.
